10:06.760 --> 10:10.600
As you may remember, one of the principal things to be discussed at this meeting, which was

10:10.600 --> 10:16.880
held in Bonn, Germany, was the arrangement for a possible citizens' conference, composed

10:16.880 --> 10:23.600
of representatives of all of the 15 NATO nations to be held later this year.

10:23.600 --> 10:30.400
And then later on, a Hague-type conference to be held in 1959 on the 10th anniversary of

10:30.400 --> 10:31.400
NATO.

10:31.400 --> 10:36.080
The reason that I was in attendance is because I'm chairman of the political committee of

10:36.080 --> 10:41.920
the conference, which produced these proposals, designed to explore ways and means to bringing

10:41.920 --> 10:48.080
the NATO nations closer together in a political and economic way for the protection of our

10:48.080 --> 10:49.080
freedom.

10:49.080 --> 10:54.240
