11:00.160 --> 11:05.920
Nevertheless, composed as it is of representatives of the people elected in their various countries

11:05.920 --> 11:12.000
to serve in their own congresses or parliament, it reflects public opinion of the countries

11:12.000 --> 11:13.800
pretty well.

